共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ad91726a40058db2a9dda82eb27e49cc2560735","tid":1543171,"uid":154872,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"內容：契弟小丑"},{"pid":"08bdc9ea2b794c4510a70b61ec893bbf71a9d047","tid":1543171,"uid":59737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82686554ed99c7259bfff715ba9782cc28f5d3ea","tid":1543171,"uid":63782,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:56:19.000Z","msg":"本書應該淨係寫住&ldquo;雲迪克&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:33:27.000Z","msg":"上冊 vvd 下冊 alisson"},{"pid":"7759b9248a670360472267ac4ac2dd529d9614a7","tid":1543171,"uid":254460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08bdc9ea2b794c4510a70b61ec893bbf71a9d047","tid":1543171,"ui